Day 17: Feature a Non-Fiction - Vincent Van Gogh is my favourite artist, so of course the non-fiction book I chose for today's challenge is about him! I bought this book when I visited Musée de Louvre last summer, it's so detailed and a wonderful read! I highly recommend it for anyone who wants to learn more about Vincent and his life 🌻🎨
----------------------------------------------------
'Van Gogh: A Life' by Steven Naifeh and Gregory White Smith, published by @randomhouse (2012)
